response: Deep learning is a machine learning technique that teaches computers to do what comes naturally to humans. It is subset of machine learning which in turn is the subset of artificial intelligence. Deep learning focuses on just a single model called neural networks. to learn more ask me about neural networks by saying what are neural networks.
